item.title: Cyber SE not happy with state of cybersecurity today
item.description:
This week we talk with Eric Jefferey, an SE for AlgoSec and host of the Cyber Greybeards podcast, and he is just a little miffed about how organizations are responding to cyber attacks today. It's not so much about how they respond to the attack itself; it's how they communicate what happened to the public â€“ if at all. He's submitting what happened at the LA Unified School District as his case in point. He's a bit fired up, so this will be a fun one.
